data.name: Paneer Tikka Kebab
data.description: Paneer Tikka is an Indian dish made from chunks of paneer marinated in spices and grilled in a tandoor.

data.name: Paneer Hariyali Kebab
data.description: Hariyali Paneer Tikka is a delectable Indian appetizer made with cubes of soft paneer, crisp bell pepper, and onions marinated in cilantro, and mint, along with yogurt and spices.

data.name: Tandoori Aloo
data.description: Tandoori Aloo or Tandoori Aloo Tikka is one of our favorite starter dishes which we order often in restaurants.

data.name: Chicken Reshmi Kebab
data.description: Reshmi is an Indian word that means 'silk'. This is an apt description for these silky-textured, delicious chicken kababs that are a traditional Mughlai dish prepared in India.

data.name: Chicken Malai Kebab
data.description: Chicken Malai refers to grilled supreme of chicken with ginger, garlic, green chilli, cream-cheese, coriander-stem and cardamom.

data.name: Chicken Tengri
data.description: A marinade of garlic, ginger, garam masala, turmeric and chilli gives chicken drumsticks a dose of sub-continental spice in Alfred Prasad's tangdi kabab recipe.

data.name: Chicken Tikka Kebab
data.description: Chicken Tikka Kebab is a delicious appetizer that is packed with flavor. It starts with chicken pieces marinated in yogurt along with lime juice and aromatic spices, then threaded onto skewers and cooked to create a delicious appetizer.

data.name: Chicken Wings
data.description: Drums, or drumettes, resemble small chicken legs, with a single, main bone running through the middle.

data.name: Mutton Kakori Kebab
data.description: Kakori Kebabs is a delicious Mughlai recipe that is prepared with mutton, onions and lots of spices. These kebabs are soft too.

data.name: Mutton Boti Kebab
data.description: Mutton Boti is a popular dish from the southern part of our country. It is made with mutton (goat meat) that is marinated in spices and then grilled.

data.name: Mutton Tikka Kebab
data.description: Mutton Boti Tikka is a popular dish from the southern part of our country. It is made with mutton (goat meat) that is marinated in spices and then grilled.

data.name: Fish Tikka Kebab
data.description: Lasooni fish tikka is one of the most delicious and flavourful dishes made from fish. The fish pieces are marinated with many herbs, spices, and yoghurt to get the best possible taste.

data.name: Prawn Tandoori
data.description: Tandoori Prawns are the grilled shrimp skewers loaded with the bold Indian flavors.
